{
  "text": "RNA extraction, library preparation, sequencing procedures, and sequencing summaries can be found in Buddenborg et al. [CITATION_1] [CITATION_2] . Illumina RNA sequencing reads underwent extensive processing in order to separate host, parasite, and potential symbiont reads.",
  "correct_citation": {
